articles.title: Astros shut out Red Sox, advance to World Series for third time in five years - Sportsnet.ca
articles.description: The Houston Astros beat the Boston Red Sox 5-0 in Game 6 of the American League Championship Series to advance to the World Series for the third time in the past five seasons.
